name: Lufthansa Cargo MD-11F [D-ALCD] Landing and Takeoff at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
What a nice surprise! Here we have one of Lufthansa Cargo's gorgeous MD-11 freighters touching down on runway 17L in some perfect morning lighting from Frankfurt with a load of 16 brand new Porsches and then leaving 8 hours later for Chicago  O'Hare. ATC is included throughout, hope you enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
